title: Mumbai: South Africa trounce India by 214 runs to win ODI series - newsR
text:
South Africa defeated India by 214 runs in the fifth and final One-Day International (ODI) match at the Wankhede Stadium in Mumbai on Sunday to clinch the series 3-2.*A jubilaint AB celebrates with du Plessis. Pic/AFP*
